articles.author: Reuters
articles.title: US targets China's chip industry with new restrictions - Reuters
articles.description: The United States on Monday launched its third big crackdown in three years on China's semiconductor industry, curbing exports to 140 companies, including chip equipment maker Naura Technology Group , among other moves.

articles.title: Researchers finally identify the ocean’s “mystery mollusk” - Ars Technica
articles.description: It’s a nudibranch, but so distantly related that it gets its own phylogenetic family.
